album.title: Blues At Sunrise

track.name: Ain't Gone 'N' Give Up On Love

artist.name: Stevie Ray Vaughan and Double Trouble

comments: Bright and light images of gentle melodies uplifting a mood. Each tune has some mystery and reticence, and the musical atmosphere makes the listener to dream.
So wonderful anytime of the day or night!!!  RIP SRV!!
Amazing guitar work as always from the best there ever was....
ma senti che pezzo, grande stevie
i would kill for this thing...
yet another awesome track on the soundtrack of my beautiful life!  Thanx for your gift, Stevie!
Stevie you were the best. You are missed and remembered!
